data.description: ***ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE AT 2.5% WITH QUALIFICATION AND APPROVAL FROM CURRENT MORTGAGE LENDER***   This totally renovated ranch home in The Terraces at Apalachee Farms shows like something out of a magazine!   Remodeled inside and out with a new 25 year roof, new water heater, new KitchenAid oven and microwave, new electric cooktop, bathrooms all remodeled with new flooring, sinks and custom vanities, new oversized garden tub in primary bathroom, new shower stalls, fixtures and tile, new flooring, light and plumbing fixtures. Interior and exterior were also just repainted. The two story foyer welcomes you into the formal dining room on the right which features wainscoting and a coffered ceiling enhanced by faux painting.  The living room with a wall of windows offers great views of the back covered patio and lush landscaping in the fenced, private backyard. A new granite faced fireplace is flanked by custom built-ins.  The primary suite has a tray ceiling and a spacious sitting room along with a new tile floor, garden tub, two custom vanities and a walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms share a full bath with a tile floor, tub/shower combo and a beautiful custom vanity.  There is also a half bath off the living room.  The breakfast area, breakfast bar and kitchen have also been updated.  Enjoy new quartz countertops, new backsplash, under counter lighting, KitchenAid dishwasher, double sinks and a walk in panty.  The laundry room has a wet sink and extra cabinets for storage. This was previously the model home for The Terraces.  The left side garage will fit a golf cart or compact auto but part of the garage was walled off to use as the model homes office.  A new owner may want to convert it back to a full size garage after closing if an office is not needed. Active swim/tennis neighborhood with great amenities including a clubhouse, three pools, playground, eight tennis courts, two pickleball courts and a picnic pavilion.
